Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:47.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103875,107837}{\i1}All I can say is\Nwhat we have is true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:49.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109005,109881}{\i1}Oh, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119557,121726}{\i1}Are you forsaking our love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122685,125980}{\i1}I'll never forget you, Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126314,128316}{\i1}Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:26.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141913,146959}It was an old movie, but I know why\NMeimi's parents recommended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146959,149170}Yes, it was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:32.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149170,152715}Gee, how I hope I find\Na love like that one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155843,158471}{\i1}He kinda looked like Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159514,161099}Meimi, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161099,162558}Huh? Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162558,166688}Let's go out and find us\Nsome fantastic boyfriends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166688,169524}Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:57.28,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:174195,177281}The Platform of Love and Tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183788,185456}And how was the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185456,187500}It was the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187500,188918}It was so touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189168,191295}It was a true love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:16.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193548,196175}They fall in love\Ndespite their differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196175,198261}But in the end, they part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198261,200054}Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:23.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200054,203307}The actor who played\NJoseph was so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205393,208396}How sickening.\NWhat's all this mush about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209063,211858}How dare you eavesdrop on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212692,213860}Humph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:38.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213860,218322}Why do girls always get so excited\Nwhen they talk about love and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218823,221617}You wouldn't understand\Nabout true love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221617,223786}And I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224537,226289}Of course you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226289,229792}All you ever think\Nabout is St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229792,231085}What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231085,232545}Well, it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:53.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232962,233963}Listen, I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233963,235506}Yeah? You're what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:57.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237133,237925}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243556,244974}{\i1}Asuka Jr.…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252982,256402}You've traveled all of\NJapan on a bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257320,258196}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:21.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258196,261699}And I met Minako here in this city\Non the last leg of my trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264160,265369}How romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265703,268164}But then his bicycle…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286724,288267}Wow, that's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288267,291771}Not really, if you have the determination,\Nyou could do it as well, Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291771,292897}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:56.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292897,296734}Since you live in Japan,\Nyou can try it anytime you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296734,298986}Then maybe I'll give it try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299237,302240}Still, I'm really glad I got to\Nmeet someone nice like you, Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302907,305952}I've met a lot of people along\Nthe way but none so nice as—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308663,309622}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312917,314168}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314168,315628}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339819,341445}Give me back my bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342655,343948}Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344365,346409}Please open this gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346409,347201}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:50.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350079,350872}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352540,353833}What is all the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:58.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354458,358170}Madame, these people\Nare demanding to be let in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362341,365428}A boy took John's bike\Nand went into the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365428,366304}That's why we…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366304,368806}Are you accusing my son Tatsuo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368806,369765}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372310,373686}You must be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373686,377732}Tatsuo has a first class American\Nbicycle, ordered especially for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378232,380860}My name is on that bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380860,382278}Please go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:23.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382278,383195}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383195,386532}I don't want to hear any more of\Nyour ridiculous accusations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386532,388284}Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390202,391329}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391329,395041}We went back several times,\Nbut no one would listen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:39.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395917,399712}And since it concerns a child, John\Ndoesn't want the police involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:46.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400254,406302}We'd been through good times\Nand bad times on our travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406302,408930}That bike was my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:54.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409972,414644}All we can do is wait for the boy to\Nreturn the bicycle on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:56.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415895,416979}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417813,419482}Let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419482,421859}I'm sure our prayers\Nwill be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:07.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424070,427740}John and Minako.\NThey're in love, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427740,429200}Yes, you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429200,430826}Such a dramatic meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:16.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431702,436832}And their love will burn furiously,\Nonly to end in a sad parting of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438209,439794}Ah, Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441504,443881}Alright.\NI'll take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443881,445841}Only we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:31.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447134,451806}John is returning to America\Non the last flight this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451806,453307}We have to get it back by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454433,455643}Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:39.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455643,459647}I'll do everything I can\Nin honor of their love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461273,462274}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464610,466278}Dad is a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466612,469699}He insists on eating oden tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472118,474370}Ah, this is my favorite…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474370,476205}I'll put a lot in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:02.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478666,482044}"I will be at the Ninomiya residence\Ntonight to retrieve a bicycle."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482044,483671}"St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489093,492638}How'd she know\Nthis was my favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493681,495307}Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503190,504775}Ruby, that's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508070,509655}Meimi, it's time for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510573,511657}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516203,518622}Yum. We're having oden tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531719,532720}Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544732,548319}There, Ruby's aerial\Nmerry-go-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548319,550196}Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:13.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551197,553616}Yes, you can use it\Nin your next magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554533,557578}Would you like\Nto be part of my show?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:36.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572718,576472}Wow, look at all this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577848,580267}Take whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582228,583938}And where's the bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584897,586232}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:53.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589110,593197}I don't care if that bike gets stolen.\NDo whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594907,597159}But isn't it supposed to be special?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597576,598744}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:06.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599954,606627}If that's how you feel, we should have given it\Nto that bothersome American.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609004,610297}Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:16.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612174,616554}Please take care of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.02,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:625020,627022}Tatsuo Ninomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628065,630985}Now, why would St. Tail\Nwant to steal this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:45.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641453,645291}Lord forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650337,651297}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:54.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653799,654967}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656927,658804}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:15.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672735,675738}In order for John\Nto make his flight tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675738,679241}he must take the train by 9 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679783,681202}9 PM at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681202,682244}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:28.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684496,688209}May God's blessings be with us.
