Comment: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:57.73,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:717738,717738}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:02.74,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:722743,722743}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:08.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723285,728123}Alright, I want this room and\Nthe house closely guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728123,729708}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:28.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747851,748477}It's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:33.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750062,753148}{\i1}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:42.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762074,762908}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767288,768455}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777381,778299}{\i1}Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779466,781302}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781969,783053}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788809,791895}{\i1}Taking what is not yours is very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791895,793355}I don't know what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793355,794898}{\i1}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802906,804658}{\i1}Now do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805117,806577}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806577,808620}It was so cool, I couldn't help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809121,810956}So you stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:33.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810956,813083}{\i1}Alright, you're forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819340,821675}St. Tail! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821675,824970}{\i1}Now for the real Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830351,832061}What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832061,833062}Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833062,834813}Somebody go check the fuse box!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834813,835939}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:10.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849578,850704}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:11.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850662,851330}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852915,854166}This is the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854166,855542}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865552,866929}Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866929,869431}A bicycle that flies…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874144,875479}Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878941,882486}Now, I'll let the wind carry me\Nright to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887699,889326}What?! You're not going to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895958,897543}Bring the patrol car around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904299,906552}Oh, yeah! I have an extra\Nballoon here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910764,913976}You're not getting away\Nthis time, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920524,921692}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923152,925946}I did it! I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925946,927448}Asuka Jr., look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959354,960314}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963275,965819}{\i1}Oh dear, I've got to\Nput Asuka Jr. down somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:16.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975579,976497}Get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976497,977623}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993472,994848}I need to borrow your bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994848,995766}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007486,1010239}Excuse me, what time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010239,1012199}Let's see… it's 8:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012199,1014117}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015452,1017120}Hey… what was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028298,1029925}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037015,1039476}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039851,1041979}Hold it! Hold it! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.98,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1041979,1043981}Tatsuo Ninomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047693,1048694}It's that kid's!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054866,1056493}Hey, who's John?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064960,1066503}Hey! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:53.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071925,1073844}Phew. That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081059,1082352}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082352,1084271}I'm not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089943,1092195}{\i1}I don't know why, but I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096700,1098160}{\i1}Oh, no!\NI've got to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104333,1106126}That's… the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127981,1130692}I want you to come to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:53.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130692,1133820}I can't, John.\NIt will just make things harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:58.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134488,1138075}{\i1}John? So that means\Nit was his bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:04.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140577,1144623}I didn't get my bike back,\Nbut I'm glad I got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144623,1145749}I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:11.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150879,1151880}I think…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153131,1154174}It's yours, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154174,1155384}But who brought it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156677,1158679}Our prayers were answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159304,1162307}John, we'll meet again, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162307,1163850}We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:28.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165227,1168814}I thought I'd never see\Nmy bike again, but I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:32.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169690,1172818}So I know you and I will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176071,1177114}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181952,1183328}{\i1}That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:55.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192629,1195048}{\i1}St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208270,1209813}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212941,1214109}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216528,1217320}Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217320,1219406}What's the matter?\NYou look so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221491,1223285}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223285,1225871}What's with you?!\NIt wouldn't hurt you to talk about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226121,1228290}Humph. It's only love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:33.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229708,1233128}Oh, so Asuka Jr. is\Nin love with somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233128,1234880}Listen here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:37.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237048,1237966}We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237966,1239342}Oh, no!
